\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {31}{\ignorespaces Part I frames intelligence as a cyclic process (ch1) driven by community architecture (ch2) and disciplined at every step by tradecraft principles and control markings (ch3). Its reader value is to make The Intelligence Cycle (ch1), Planning and Direction, Collection, and Processing visible at a glance, with the foundations of intelligence tradecraft section as the source section and defensive review as the boundary.}}{163}{figure.caption.33}\protected@file@percent }
