\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {41}{\ignorespaces The unit module map traces the part's chapters as a linear reading sequence. Its reader value is to make 2 module nodes in the unit's ordered, source-backed reading sequence from its first module to its last visible at a glance, with the signals intelligence sigint section as the source section and defensive review as the boundary.}}{272}{figure.caption.43}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:part-signals-intelligence-sigint-module-map}{{41}{272}{The unit module map traces the part's chapters as a linear reading sequence. Its reader value is to make 2 module nodes in the unit's ordered, source-backed reading sequence from its first module to its last visible at a glance, with the signals intelligence sigint section as the source section and defensive review as the boundary}{figure.caption.43}{}}
\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {42}{\ignorespaces Part III shows SIGINT as a legally gated, layered pipeline where authorities and minimization rules govern collection disciplines (ch7), feed a processing stack into cryptanalysis (ch8), with the modern crypto frontier reshaping what is feasible. In the signals intelligence sigint section, it lets readers compare Legal and Authorization Gate, Collection Authorities and Warrants, Minimization and Privacy Rules, and SIGINT Disciplines, ch7 so the visual functions as a traceable course aid rather than an unscoped assertion.}}{273}{figure.caption.44}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:part-sigint-authorized-stack}{{42}{273}{Part III shows SIGINT as a legally gated, layered pipeline where authorities and minimization rules govern collection disciplines (ch7), feed a processing stack into cryptanalysis (ch8), with the modern crypto frontier reshaping what is feasible. In the signals intelligence sigint section, it lets readers compare Legal and Authorization Gate, Collection Authorities and Warrants, Minimization and Privacy Rules, and SIGINT Disciplines, ch7 so the visual functions as a traceable course aid rather than an unscoped assertion}{figure.caption.44}{}}
